				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"></span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Nadia wrote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote"></span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">(epic) Rune is stackable and mana free, I like it. The trigger effect needs to (and is next patch) be changed so that when it wears off it doesn't agro every mob near you kos or not. </td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
